{"tid":1954221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田康林苑39歲男子墮樓屍身發臭 警指無可疑","createTime":"2020-04-01T16:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T03:19:55.000Z","uid":29627,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb9408d4b1249264c6c24d536559789add3da28","tid":1954221,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"沙田康林苑39歲男子墮樓屍身發臭 警指無可疑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200401/large/1585736036_e423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200401%2Flarge%2F1585736036_e423.jpg&h=63e3ea1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中午12時許，警方接獲報案，指一名男子倒卧於沙田康林苑景林閣平台，懷疑他從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報到場，現場證實該男子死亡，屍身已經發臭。警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信該男子39歲，從上址一大堂墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200401/67JQ435WO3Q4Q6TE3KC72WNFQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200401%2F67JQ435WO3Q4Q6TE3KC72WNFQA%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=7d6e54bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200401%2F67JQ435WO3Q4Q6TE3KC72WNFQA%2F&h=da4bc703\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200401/67JQ435WO3Q4Q6TE3KC72WNFQA/</a>"},{"pid":"c630dbf6a8a13bddd04f2ef9a02cdf3349f8047a","tid":1954221,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65915dddd2927fc2de79d22014ac15ccaf40a590","tid":1954221,"uid":52946,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"發臭但無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff63ac080052aabc3034309222f3976f33a22d9","tid":1954221,"uid":1654,"like":25,"dislike":0,